<section id="changelog:umc">
	<title>Univention Management Console</title>

	<section id="changelog:umc:web">
	  <title>Univention Management Console web interface</title>
	  <itemizedlist>
		<listitem><simpara>
		  A display bug was resolved which showed scrollbars in the search input field in the user
		  module when using the Chrome browser (<ulink url="&ucsbug;35838">Bug 35838</ulink>).
		</simpara></listitem>

		<listitem><simpara>
		  A display but was resolved which caused the login button to be displaced when using
		  the Firefox browser (<ulink url="&ucsbug;34071">Bug 34071</ulink>).
		</simpara></listitem>

		<listitem><simpara>
		  Open the <guimenu>Software Update</guimenu> UMC module upon startup during release updates
		  and show a information dialog about the current update process (<ulink
		  url="&ucsbug;37255">Bug 37255</ulink>).
		</simpara></listitem>

	  </itemizedlist>
	</section>


	<section id="changelog:umc:server">
	  <title>Univention Management Console server</title>
	  <itemizedlist>
		<listitem><simpara>
		  Fix an error introduced in UCS 3.2-3 regarding the error handling of closed UMC
		  module process sockets (<ulink url="&ucsbug;36561">Bug 36561</ulink>).
		</simpara></listitem>
		
		<listitem><simpara>
		  Fixed a bug which prevented that UMC components could write into their logfiles (<ulink
		  url="&ucsbug;37159">Bug 37159</ulink>, <ulink url="&ucsbug;37316">Bug 37316</ulink>).
		</simpara></listitem>

		<listitem><simpara>
		  Fix an error if the UMC server and the UMC module want to close the module process at the
		  same time (<ulink url="&ucsbug;37315">Bug 37315</ulink>).
		</simpara></listitem>

		<listitem><simpara>
		  Fixed handling of crashed UMC module processes (<ulink url="&ucsbug;37379">Bug
		  37379</ulink>, <ulink url="&ucsbug;37380">Bug 37380</ulink>).
		</simpara></listitem>

	  </itemizedlist>
	</section>

	<section id="changelog:umc:appcenter">
	  <title>Univention App Center</title>
	  <itemizedlist>
		<listitem><simpara>
		  A command to allow searching for multiple components at once has been added (<ulink
		  url="&ucsbug;37029">Bug 37029</ulink>).
		</simpara></listitem>

		<listitem><simpara>
		  The translation file for installed apps modules may have been corrupted during a release
		  update. This has been fixed (<ulink url="&ucsbug;36657">Bug 36657</ulink>).
		</simpara></listitem>

		</itemizedlist>
	</section>


	<section id="changelog:umc:setup">
	  <title>Basic settings / Appliance mode</title>
	  <itemizedlist>
		<listitem><simpara>
		  Fix the configuration of primary devices and MII monitoring in bonding network devices
		  (<ulink url="&ucsbug;36339">Bug 36339</ulink>, <ulink url="&ucsbug;36341">Bug
		  36341</ulink>).
		</simpara></listitem>
	  </itemizedlist>
	</section>


	<section id="changelog:umc:user">
		<title>Users module</title>
		<itemizedlist>
		  <listitem><simpara>
			Simple authentication accounts can now be created much faster (the unnecessary UID
			locking is now omitted for these accounts) (<ulink url="&ucsbug;34811">Bug
			34811</ulink>).
		  </simpara></listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
	</section>


